# ── stats ──
msgid ""
"usage: ring stats [--since DURATION]\n"
"\n"
"等待統計：最近一段時間各專案讓你回應的次數與 🔴 等待時長（平均 / 最長 / 總計）。\n"
"資料來自 hook 寫的狀態轉換 log（~/.config/ring/events.jsonl），zero-config 測不到等待。\n"
"\n"
"options:\n"
"  --since DURATION  統計時間窗（例如 12h、7d、30d；預設 7d）\n"
msgstr ""
"usage: ring stats [--since DURATION]\n"
"\n"
"Waiting stats: per-project counts and 🔴 wait durations (avg / max / total) for a recent window.\n"
"Data comes from the hook-written transition log (~/.config/ring/events.jsonl);\n"
"zero-config cannot detect waits.\n"
"\n"
"options:\n"
"  --since DURATION  stats window (e.g. 12h, 7d, 30d; default 7d)\n"

msgid "等待統計：你讓 agent 🔴 等了多久。"
msgstr "Waiting stats: how long you kept agents 🔴 waiting."

msgid "統計時間窗（例如 12h、7d、30d；預設 7d）"
msgstr "stats window (e.g. 12h, 7d, 30d; default 7d)"

msgid "無效的 --since：{value}"
msgstr "invalid --since: {value}"

msgid "🎤 RiNG stats — 最近 {since} 的 🔴 等待"
msgstr "🎤 RiNG stats — 🔴 waits in the last {since}"

msgid "（這段時間沒有等待紀錄。stats 需要 hook 模式：ring install-hooks）"
msgstr "(no waiting records in this window. stats needs hook mode: ring install-hooks)"

msgid "全部"
msgstr "total"

msgid "次數"
msgstr "waits"

msgid "平均"
msgstr "avg"

msgid "最長"
msgstr "max"

msgid "總等待"
msgstr "total wait"

msgid "⚠️ 其中 {n} 段還在 🔴 等你（計到現在為止）。"
msgstr "⚠️ {n} of these are still 🔴 waiting for you (counted up to now)."
